1
00:00:01,480 --> 00:00:06,610
Edolas's King Faust ordered the merciless 
annihilation of all in his way.

2
00:00:06,980 --> 00:00:14,110
Lucy, Gray, and the members of Edolas's 
Fairy Tail all stood up against the Royal Army.

3
00:00:14,820 --> 00:00:19,050
The three Dragon Slayers, 
Natsu, Gajeel, and Wendy,

4
00:00:19,050 --> 00:00:25,580
battle Droma Anim, a hardened 
armor that Faust is piloting.

5
00:02:04,860 --> 00:02:08,110
Wizards of Earthland!

6
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:13,450
Those who possess within them an eternal, 
never-ending supply of magic power...

7
00:02:13,450 --> 00:02:20,400
And among them, you Dragon Wizards 
and your ridiculous magic!

8
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:26,110
Hand your magic power over 
to me! This world demands it!

9
00:02:30,730 --> 00:02:34,340
Fall down to earth, dragons!

10
00:02:36,860 --> 00:02:46,850
As long as we have this ultimate magic 
weapon, Droma Anim, our army will never be destroyed!

11
00:02:58,770 --> 00:03:00,920
Getting up again?

12
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:03,060
Impressive...

13
00:03:03,060 --> 00:03:05,910
That magic power is incredible!

14
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:09,830
Dragon Wizards, you will be ours!

15
00:03:16,390 --> 00:03:19,320
I'm Standing Here!

16
00:03:34,570 --> 00:03:37,140
Collect more magic power!

17
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:42,780
Droma Anim, collect magic power 
from the sky and the land!

18
00:03:52,460 --> 00:03:57,870
I can feel it... This world is 
running out of magic power...

19
00:03:58,490 --> 00:04:03,220
And that is precisely why you must be ours!

20
00:04:05,590 --> 00:04:08,430
Salamander, use your breath.

21
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,500
You too, brat!

22
00:04:10,790 --> 00:04:12,740
All three at the same time?

23
00:04:12,740 --> 00:04:16,560
I didn't want to suggest it 'cause 
I'm not sure what'll happen.

24
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:18,610
But we got no choice!

25
00:04:18,610 --> 00:04:19,980
Understood!

26
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:21,230
All right!

27
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,840
Roar of the...

28
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:26,980
Roar of the...

29
00:04:26,980 --> 00:04:28,160
Roar of the...

30
00:04:29,420 --> 00:04:32,190
Their magic power is rising again?

31
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:35,710
Fire Dragon!

32
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:35,710
Iron Dragon!

33
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:35,710
Sky Dragon!

34
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,100
Did that do it?

35
00:05:00,150 --> 00:05:01,110
Above!

36
00:05:06,570 --> 00:05:08,820
It could jump that high?

37
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:12,580
Oh, no! Our triple roar didn't hit!

38
00:05:12,580 --> 00:05:14,080
We'll do it again!

39
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:16,040
You won't get a chance!

40
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:20,930
Dragon Knight Spread Cannon!

41
00:05:36,140 --> 00:05:39,900
For the world... For our Edolas...

42
00:05:40,230 --> 00:05:43,810
That's the difference between you and I.

43
00:05:43,810 --> 00:05:48,420
You said that you didn't know anything 
about this world, didn't you?

44
00:05:48,420 --> 00:05:55,670
What the living creatures of this world 
require aren't guilds... It's eternal magic power!

45
00:05:56,650 --> 00:05:58,880
It's required by the citizens.

46
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:04,450
You don't have any of the 
burden of responsibility!

47
00:06:10,590 --> 00:06:14,350
This is bad... My magic power is... almost...

48
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:16,520
Looks like you're running on empty.

49
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:34,530
No matter how infinite it may be, it takes 
time to regenerate once used up, yes?

50
00:06:35,220 --> 00:06:39,660
Now don't struggle, and become 
the magic power of our world!

51
00:06:40,170 --> 00:06:45,550
How well you are treated will 
depend on your attitude.

52
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:50,050
It's no use... I can't stand up...

53
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:52,010
Is this the end?

54
00:06:57,570 --> 00:06:58,930
Don't give up!

55
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:03,200
It ain't over yet!

56
00:07:04,020 --> 00:07:07,080
Bring it on, you bastard!

57
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:10,780
I'm standin' right here!

58
00:07:13,010 --> 00:07:15,660
You are one obstinate brat!

59
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,950
Natsu-san...

60
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:24,210
Fool... What can you do 
without any magic power?

61
00:07:24,210 --> 00:07:25,880
I squeeze it out!

62
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:28,460
Natsu-san!

63
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:35,510
I squeeze it out from tomorrow's!

64
00:07:45,230 --> 00:07:48,190
Don't underestimate a Dragon Slayer!

65
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:53,740
From... tomorrow's?

66
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:57,990
Then I'll beat it into you!

67
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:04,420
You'll learn just who I am!

68
00:08:05,980 --> 00:08:07,040
What?

69
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:09,910
We don't need to combine our powers!

70
00:08:09,910 --> 00:08:14,260
All we need is our power, 
our wishes, to be as one!

71
00:08:17,110 --> 00:08:17,970
My foot...

72
00:08:17,970 --> 00:08:21,850
Locked down! Now you can't 
escape into the air!

73
00:08:23,170 --> 00:08:25,250
Damn you!

74
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:28,370
Go, Salamander!

75
00:08:28,370 --> 00:08:30,410
It's got to be you!

76
00:08:30,410 --> 00:08:32,690
You do it!

77
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:37,950
Wendy!

78
00:08:38,950 --> 00:08:41,290
Roar towards me!

79
00:08:41,290 --> 00:08:43,540
Stand up!!

80
00:08:43,540 --> 00:08:45,000
Right!

81
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,630
I believe in you, Natsu-san!

82
00:08:49,820 --> 00:08:52,320
You stubborn little... Get off!

83
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:54,500
Never, you pile of scrap!

84
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:10,740
Roar of the... Sky Dragon!!

85
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:21,830
Do it... Use the special 
vortex of her breath, and...

86
00:09:34,730 --> 00:09:38,960
Is this... a fantasy?

87
00:09:39,970 --> 00:09:43,670
Sword Edge of the Fire Dragon!

88
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:40,700
Is... Is this what I desired?

89
00:10:59,510 --> 00:11:02,700
S-Save me...

90
00:11:22,860 --> 00:11:25,260
We defeated the King!

91
00:11:25,260 --> 00:11:27,810
What do you call that again? Checkmate?

92
00:11:27,810 --> 00:11:31,540
You're supposed to say that 
<i>before</i> you capture the king!

93
00:11:32,090 --> 00:11:33,040
Idiot.

94
00:11:35,660 --> 00:11:37,250
W-What's that?

95
00:11:37,250 --> 00:11:39,780
Reinforcements?

96
00:11:40,180 --> 00:11:43,880
You've gotta be kiddin' me... I'm 
<i>really</i> out of magic power now.

97
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:46,640
No, it's not... It's...

98
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:53,390
The floating islands are falling.

99
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:17,880
What's this? The islands in the sky are...

100
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:20,170
Whoa, whoa! What's happening?

101
00:12:21,290 --> 00:12:23,290
We're in big trouble!

102
00:12:27,390 --> 00:12:29,140
This is bad.

103
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:34,200
The floating islands of Edolas work 
using the world's magic power.

104
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:37,570
So if they are falling, that means...

105
00:12:37,570 --> 00:12:42,090
The magic is disappearing from this world.

106
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,340
What's happening?

107
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:51,640
I don't know... But, this is...

108
00:12:54,630 --> 00:12:58,420
This is... magic power?

109
00:12:58,420 --> 00:13:00,940
Why is this happening?

110
00:13:18,650 --> 00:13:21,000
The time has finally come...

111
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,770
Byro!

112
00:13:23,650 --> 00:13:26,110
Oh, it's you two.

113
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:29,000
Pretty, don't you think?

114
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,830
Pretty? What do you mean, Sugar Boy?

115
00:13:31,830 --> 00:13:33,950
I mean the magic power...

116
00:13:33,950 --> 00:13:40,900
I expected flowing magic 
power to be more... fearsome.

117
00:13:45,350 --> 00:13:46,510
Prince...

118
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,690
This will do.

119
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:52,470
As long as there is magic power, 
people will fight over it.

120
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:56,010
Therefore I will rid this 
world of magic completely.

121
00:13:58,120 --> 00:14:04,020
The Anima I have set in reverse will flow 
all the magic power from Edolas to Earthland.

122
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:07,260
In Earthland, already overflowing with magic,

123
00:14:07,260 --> 00:14:10,990
this magic power will quickly be 
transformed into a part of nature there.

124
00:14:12,450 --> 00:14:17,110
To create a new world, I will 
destroy a portion of Edolas.

125
00:14:24,110 --> 00:14:26,310
I can't use my weapon any more!

126
00:14:26,310 --> 00:14:27,760
What's going on?

127
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:29,550
Same over here!

128
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:31,340
What'll we do?

129
00:14:31,340 --> 00:14:33,200
My weapon's broken!

130
00:14:38,950 --> 00:14:40,700
What's happening?

131
00:14:40,980 --> 00:14:43,730
My weapon! My weapon!

132
00:14:43,730 --> 00:14:45,160
Calm down!

133
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:49,360
It's over... The world is ending...

134
00:14:50,010 --> 00:14:51,510
Carla...

135
00:14:59,010 --> 00:15:01,040
That's magic power!

136
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:02,370
Magic power?

137
00:15:02,370 --> 00:15:05,630
Won't losing all the magic 
power be a big problem?

138
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:19,140
Retreat!

139
00:15:19,140 --> 00:15:22,060
If we can't use our weapons, we're screwed!

140
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:24,380
The Royal Army's...

141
00:15:24,380 --> 00:15:25,760
...run away!

142
00:15:26,090 --> 00:15:28,070
Hey guys, we did it!

143
00:15:30,430 --> 00:15:32,460
We're finished!

144
00:15:32,460 --> 00:15:36,200
Magic power is disappearing... 
We can't use magic anymore...

145
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:38,830
Everything is coming to an end...

146
00:15:38,830 --> 00:15:40,140
So, today is the day...

147
00:15:40,140 --> 00:15:41,590
What should we do?

148
00:15:41,590 --> 00:15:44,940
What's going to happen to us? To the guild?

149
00:15:44,940 --> 00:15:49,340
There's no such thing as a wizard's 
guild that can't use magic!

150
00:15:49,590 --> 00:15:52,870
Everyone calm down! It'll be okay!

151
00:15:52,870 --> 00:15:54,510
Like hell it will!

152
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:58,330
The magic power is disappearing 
from the world! All of it!

153
00:15:58,330 --> 00:16:00,930
What's gonna happen to our wizard guild?

154
00:16:00,930 --> 00:16:06,480
It's over... We may have won the 
battle, but we lost the world.

155
00:16:06,820 --> 00:16:11,510
The thing Juvia feared most of 
all... Magic power drying up...

156
00:16:12,760 --> 00:16:16,450
Magic is vanishing! Magic 
power is disappearing!

157
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:18,590
It's too late!

158
00:16:18,590 --> 00:16:19,970
Save us!

159
00:16:19,970 --> 00:16:21,740
What'll we do?

160
00:16:21,740 --> 00:16:23,510
It's the end of the world!

161
00:16:23,510 --> 00:16:25,890
Edolas's final day...

162
00:16:25,890 --> 00:16:27,750
Wait a second, everyone!

163
00:16:28,650 --> 00:16:34,170
I can't believe it... Magic 
power is vanishing from Edolas.

164
00:16:34,590 --> 00:16:37,640
Everything is coming to an end.

165
00:16:53,460 --> 00:16:57,370
Dad... All the floating 
islands are falling...

166
00:16:57,370 --> 00:16:59,410
It's all over...

167
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:07,610
Where do they think they're running?

168
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:11,250
To us, Edolas is everything.

169
00:17:14,950 --> 00:17:19,300
Magic power is flowing from 
the land into the sky.

170
00:17:19,300 --> 00:17:20,510
Grandma...

171
00:17:20,510 --> 00:17:24,520
Is this punishment for opposing the Exceed?

172
00:17:26,150 --> 00:17:27,480
It's started.

173
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:29,650
Nothing's started.

174
00:17:29,650 --> 00:17:30,900
It's ending.

175
00:17:31,390 --> 00:17:33,610
Edolas is finished.

176
00:17:35,300 --> 00:17:37,360
And it's happening so simply...

177
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:42,870
The Royal City, Edolas... 
History itself is ending.

178
00:17:42,870 --> 00:17:47,240
Can you even imagine a world without magic?

179
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:52,120
I don't know... I haven't 
ever thought about it.

180
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:59,840
Not just us... Can the people 
in town imagine it themselves?

181
00:18:11,980 --> 00:18:15,710
Grandma, watch out! The rivers 
in the sky are falling!

182
00:18:15,710 --> 00:18:18,430
The world is finished...

183
00:18:19,050 --> 00:18:20,820
Let's head back to the 
city around the castle!

184
00:18:20,820 --> 00:18:22,470
What're you planning to do?

185
00:18:22,470 --> 00:18:24,660
I'm worried about the people in the city!

186
00:18:24,660 --> 00:18:28,030
There might be something that we can do!

187
00:18:28,030 --> 00:18:31,700
Yeah... I think I understand what you mean.

188
00:18:31,700 --> 00:18:32,790
Okay, then.

189
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:36,000
Please wait!

190
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:46,720
Is this world finished?

191
00:18:51,650 --> 00:18:54,190
I can't believe you really did it.

192
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,660
But...

193
00:18:59,150 --> 00:19:03,600
I know... The citizens will be in a panic.

194
00:19:04,580 --> 00:19:09,160
Not many humans can adapt so 
quickly to a changing world...

195
00:19:18,130 --> 00:19:21,090
My fire lacrima broke!

196
00:19:22,140 --> 00:19:25,700
That's why they need a new leader.

197
00:19:26,830 --> 00:19:29,600
A new king for a new world.

198
00:19:31,930 --> 00:19:34,910
To soothe the unease of the citizens,

199
00:19:34,910 --> 00:19:36,540
and lead them to happiness...

200
00:19:36,540 --> 00:19:37,860
A new king.

201
00:19:37,860 --> 00:19:40,670
I see. And it will be you, Prince?

202
00:19:40,670 --> 00:19:43,570
No. Not me.

203
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:47,750
That would not be possible for me, 
who did not walk with this world.

204
00:19:48,360 --> 00:19:50,400
Furthermore, I have no right.

205
00:19:51,970 --> 00:19:57,170
To calm the rioting masses, we need someone 
to play both the hero, and the villain.

206
00:19:58,170 --> 00:20:00,170
Villain and hero?

207
00:20:02,850 --> 00:20:06,050
The one who exposes and punishes the villain

208
00:20:06,050 --> 00:20:08,790
who plunged the world into 
chaos will become a hero,

209
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:11,930
and that hero will unite the people.

210
00:20:12,670 --> 00:20:14,060
He'll become king.

211
00:20:17,180 --> 00:20:20,100
Hey! The water lacrima disappeared!

212
00:20:20,100 --> 00:20:21,780
Same with the fire lacrima in my house!

213
00:20:21,780 --> 00:20:23,570
My vehicle won't move!

214
00:20:23,570 --> 00:20:25,740
The wind lacrima isn't working!

215
00:20:25,740 --> 00:20:27,050
No!

216
00:20:27,050 --> 00:20:28,660
What's happening?

217
00:20:29,280 --> 00:20:33,660
W-Who will be the villain and the hero?

218
00:20:33,660 --> 00:20:35,920
You already know that, don't you?

219
00:20:36,330 --> 00:20:42,630
I am the evil villain who overthrew the king 
and stole the magic power from this world.

220
00:20:43,330 --> 00:20:47,290
And you are suited to heal 
the misunderstandings

221
00:20:47,290 --> 00:20:49,350
and prejudice between the races...

222
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:54,860
You will execute me, the one 
who destroyed the world!

223
00:20:55,270 --> 00:20:58,950
And then you will become the world's king!

224
00:21:04,310 --> 00:21:07,390
God, please save us!

225
00:21:16,690 --> 00:21:20,080
Hey, you! This isn't time to be taking notes!

226
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:24,100
We are now standing up against 
the end of the world.

227
00:21:24,100 --> 00:21:28,100
As a living being of Edolas, I 
must record all that happens.

228
00:21:28,430 --> 00:21:29,720
Suit yourself!

229
00:21:37,090 --> 00:21:43,080
You must execute me, the one who caused this 
turmoil, in front of the panicking citizens.

230
00:21:43,730 --> 00:21:48,860
As a member of the Royal 
Army... As an Exceed...

231
00:21:49,470 --> 00:21:52,830
Quell the panic, and lead the people.

232
00:21:53,270 --> 00:21:58,210
Become King of a new world, 
without magic power.

233
00:22:14,330 --> 00:22:19,890
How could you seriously say 
such nonsense, Prince?!

234
00:23:55,980 --> 00:23:59,280
What'll happen to this world when 
all the magic power is gone?

235
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:00,980
I can't imagine it.

236
00:24:00,980 --> 00:24:05,380
It's a world unlike ours, where 
everything revolves around magic.

237
00:24:05,380 --> 00:24:08,250
But what's most important 
isn't magic power, right?

238
00:24:08,250 --> 00:24:13,510
Isn't what's most important the friends 
that help and believe in each other?

239
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:16,510
Next time: Bye-bye, Edolas.

240
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:19,890
Sometimes even you have 
a way with words, Natsu!

241
00:24:19,890 --> 00:24:22,180
There was a jab in there, wasn't there?!

242
00:24:22,180 --> 00:24:24,520
Not at all. I was complimenting you.

243
00:24:24,520 --> 00:24:26,520


